title: "Fable Think: an open cognitive operating system for AI models and agents"
type: software
authors:
  - name: "Fable Think contributors"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/fable-think/fable-think"
url: "https://github.com/fable-think/fable-think"
version: 0.1.0-dev
date-released: "2026-07-12"
keywords:
  - cognitive architecture
  - AI agents
  - verification
  - self-repair
  - agent skills
  - abstention
abstract: >-
  Fable Think is an open cognitive operating system for AI models and agents.
  It separates thinking, inspection, repair, verification, evidence, and
  continuation into distinct operations, supports abstention as a first-class
  result, and attaches an explicit evidence level to every capability claim.
  Fable Think is an independent open-source project. It is not affiliated with
  or endorsed by Anthropic.
